FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE AND NONINFRINGEMENT. IN NO EVENT SHALL THE
AUTHORS OR COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES OR OTHER
LIABILITY, WHETHER IN AN ACTION OF CONTRACT, TORT OR OTHERWISE, ARISING FROM,
OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH THE SOFTWARE OR THE USE OR OTHER DEALINGS IN THE
SOFTWARE.</pre>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-border/20" />

      <!-- Noto Serif SC -->
      <section>
        <h4 class="text-base font-serif-cn font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">2. Noto Serif SC / 思源宋体</h4>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">来源：</span>Google Fonts — <a href="https://fonts.google.com/noto/specimen/Noto+Serif+SC" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">https://fonts.google.com/noto/specimen/Noto+Serif+SC</a></p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">版权所有：</span>© Adobe (<a href="http://www.adobe.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">http://www.adobe.com/</a>), with Reserved Font Name 'Source'</p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">许可证：</span>SIL Open Font License 1.1</p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">用途：</span>网站正文字体（未随本网站分发，仅通过 Google Fonts 在线引用）</p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs bg-bg-main/40 p-2 rounded">
          说明：本网站未直接分发该字体文件，仅通过 Google Fonts 服务在页面渲染时加载。根据 SIL OFL 1.1，保留上述名称、版权及许可证声明即可。
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-border/20" />

      <!-- JetBrains Mono -->
      <section>
        <h4 class="text-base font-serif-cn font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">3. JetBrains Mono</h4>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">来源：</span>Google Fonts — <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/JetBrains+Mono" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">https://fonts.google.com/specimen/JetBrains+Mono</a></p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">版权所有：</span>JetBrains s.r.o.</p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">许可证：</span>SIL Open Font License 1.1</p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary">用途：</span>代码/等宽字体（未随本网站分发，仅通过 Google Fonts 在线引用）</p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs bg-bg-main/40 p-2 rounded">
          说明：本网站未直接分发该字体文件，仅通过 Google Fonts 服务在页面渲染时加载。根据 SIL OFL 1.1，保留上述名称、版权及许可证声明即可。
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-border/20" />

      <!-- Astro -->
      <section>
        <h4 class="text-base font-serif-cn font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">4. Astro</h4>
        <div class="space-y-1">
