          <p><span class="text-text-primary">用途：</span>Astro 的 Tailwind CSS 集成（仅用于开发构建，不包含在最终产品中）</p>
        </div>
        <pre class="mt-3 p-3 bg-bg-main/60 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-words text-text-secondary">MIT License

